###############################################################################
# Coleção de requisições da API de Despesas Pessoais
#
# Como usar:
#   1) Instale a extensão "REST Client" (Huachao Mao) no VSCode.
#   2) Suba o ambiente: docker compose up -d
#   3) Clique em "Send Request" (aparece acima de cada requisição).
#
# O token do login é capturado automaticamente (variável {{authToken}}),
# então basta rodar o LOGIN uma vez e as demais chamadas já usam o token.
###############################################################################

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

# Token capturado da resposta do login (ver requisição @name login abaixo)
@authToken = {{login.response.body.$.token}}
# Id da despesa criada (ver requisição @name criarDespesa abaixo)
@expenseId = {{criarDespesa.response.body.$.expense.id}}


### 1) Registrar usuário  (espera 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "teste@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "password_confirm": "secret123"
}


### 2) Login  (espera 200 + token)  -> roda esta ANTES das rotas protegidas
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "teste@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}


### 3) Criar despesa  (espera 201)  -> o acento "ç" funciona aqui (envio UTF-8)
# @name criarDespesa
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "description": "Almoço no centro",
  "category": "alimentacao",
  "amount": 42.90,
  "expense_date": "2026-07-10"
}


### 4) Criar uma segunda despesa (transporte, mês diferente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "description": "Uber",
  "category": "transporte",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "expense_date": "2026-06-15"
}


### 5) Listar todas as despesas  (espera itens + pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 6) Filtrar por categoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?category=alimentacao
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 7) Filtrar por período (mês/ano)
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?year=2026&month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 8) Ordenar por data ascendente + paginação
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?sort=asc&page=1&per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9) Detalhar uma despesa pelo id
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 10) Editar despesa (PATCH — pode alterar qualquer campo)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "amount": 99.99,
  "category": "lazer"
}


### 11) Excluir despesa  (espera 204 sem corpo)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/expenses/{{expenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


###############################################################################
# Casos de erro (para demonstrar as validações)
###############################################################################

### 12) Sem token  (espera 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses


### 13) Categoria inválida  (espera 422 + errors)
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "description": "Curso de PHP",
  "category": "educacao",
  "amount": 100,
  "expense_date": "2026-01-01"
}


### 14) Filtrar por mês sem informar o ano  (espera 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?month=6
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
